      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·001.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鹿鳴.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>呦呦鹿鳴，食野之芩。我有嘉賓，鼓瑟鼓琴。
鼓瑟鼓琴，和樂且湛。我有旨酒，以燕樂嘉賓之心。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>With pleased sounds the deer call to one another,
Eating the salsola of the fields.
I have here admirable guests,
To feast and make glad their hearts.
The pleasant sound of their lutes,
The reverence of their deportment,
The excellence of their virtuous fame,
Make the people imitate them.
They have good wine,
By which they entertain their admirable guests,
To feast and make glad their hearts.</seg>
      </tuv>
